'''海力·格布列塞拉希'''（{{Lang-am|'''ኃይሌ ገብረ ሥላሴ'''}}，haylē gebre silassē；{{lang-en|'''Haile Gebrselassie'''}}，{{bd|1973年|4月18日||}}），亦有部份香港媒體譯作'''基比拉沙'''<ref name="apple_daily">{{cite news| language =zh-hk| author =| coauthors =| url =http://www1.appledaily.atnext.com//template/apple/art_main.cfm?iss_id=20080311&sec_id=25391&subsec_id=25392&art_id=10851298| title =奧運　基比拉沙棄戰京奧馬拉松| work =體育| publisher =[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]| pages =| date =2008-03-11| accessdate =2008-07-30| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080922214833/http://www1.appledaily.atnext.com/template/apple/art_main.cfm?iss_id=20080311&sec_id=25391&subsec_id=25392&art_id=10851298| archivedate =2008-09-22}}</ref>、'''基比斯拉斯'''<ref name="sing_tao">{{cite news | language = zh-hk | author = | coauthors = | url = http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/080311/3/5qns.html | title = 「大部制」理順權責　亦要做好問責 | work = 社評 | publisher = [[星島日報|星島日報]] | pages = | date = 2008-03-12 | accessdate = 2008-07-30}}</ref>，[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚]][[长跑|长跑]]运动员，他曾是[[马拉松|马拉松]]、[[10公里馬拉松|10公里馬拉松]]、[[20000公尺賽跑|20000公尺賽跑]]、[[半程馬拉松|半程馬拉松]]和[[1小時限時跑|1小時限時跑]][[世界纪录|世界纪录]]保持者。

== 宣佈放棄參加2008年北京奧運馬拉松賽事 ==

2008年3月10日，基比沙拉錫宣布，由於[[北京市|北京市]][[空氣污染|空氣污染]]問題嚴重，故不參加[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]的[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會田徑比賽|馬拉松賽事]]，避免其[[哮喘|哮喘]]病發，但他仍會參加10,000米賽事。<ref name="apple_daily" /><ref name="sing_tao" /><ref>{{cite news | language = en | author =  | coauthors =  | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2008/SPORT/03/10/athletics.marathon/ | title = Gebreselassie likely to miss Beijing marathon | work = World Sport | publisher = [[CNN.com|CNN.com]] | pages =  | date = 2008-03-10 | accessdate = 2008-07-30 | archive-date = 2019-06-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608065240/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/SPORT/03/10/athletics.marathon/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language = en | author =  | coauthors =  | url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/sport/archives/2008/03/19/2003406265 | title = Gebreselassie will not run in Beijing's Olympic marathon | work = 體育 | publisher = [[台北時報|台北時報]] | pages =  | date = 2008-03-19 | accessdate = 2008-07-30 | archive-date = 2020-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200808113642/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/sport/archives/2008/03/19/2003406265 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language = zh-hk | author = | coauthors = | url = http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/080405/4/2zw9.html | title = 法總統提出席奧運3條件 | work = 兩岸 | publisher = [[明報|明報]] | pages = | date = 2008-04-05 | accessdate = 2008-07-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language = en | author = Addis Ababa | coauthors = | url = http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20080725/wl_africa_afp/oly2008athleticsethgebrselassie_080725170621 | title = Gebrselassie says he's fit for final Olympic showdown | work = 非洲 | publisher = [[法國新聞社|法國新聞社]] | pages = | date = 2008-07-25 | accessdate = 2008-07-30}}</ref>

